20#ifndef GCC_LTO_SECTION_NAMES_H
21#define GCC_LTO_SECTION_NAMES_H
22
23/* The string that is the prefix on the section names we make for lto.
24 For decls the DECL_ASSEMBLER_NAME is appended to make the section
25 name for the functions and static_initializers. For other types of
26 sections a '.' and the section type are appended. */
27#define LTO_SECTION_NAME_PREFIX ".gnu.lto_"
28#define OFFLOAD_SECTION_NAME_PREFIX ".gnu.offload_lto_"
29
30/* Can be either OFFLOAD_SECTION_NAME_PREFIX when we stream IR for offload
31 compiler, or LTO_SECTION_NAME_PREFIX for LTO case. */
32extern const char *section_name_prefix;
33
34/* Segment name for LTO sections. This is only used for Mach-O. */
35
36#define LTO_SEGMENT_NAME "__GNU_LTO"
37
38#define OFFLOAD_VAR_TABLE_SECTION_NAME ".gnu.offload_vars"
39#define OFFLOAD_FUNC_TABLE_SECTION_NAME ".gnu.offload_funcs"
40
41#endif /* GCC_LTO_SECTION_NAMES_H */
